7:
After me, Dragon Slayer! Winds of
Fortune!
17:
That tentacle thing is what's driving
the monsters crazy! Don't let it get
away!
26:
She's beauty, she's grace! She'll
shoot you in the face! Levin Rainfall!
32:
Hehe, now that's the Celestial Blitz
we all know and love. No need to
help on that front.
35:
There are two more to the
southwest. Go, now...
39:
Your Highness, I bring news! The
lands between here and the
northern canal are clear of the
terrors!
40:
The Tempest's squadron is heading
east, while the Celestial Blitz's
squadron is returning to rendezvous!
46:
You have some incredible friends,
Yuwel!
49: I really do. I am lucky to have them.
53:
Which is why I can't let them do all
the work. We must prove ourselves
no less capable, Your Highness!
67: Break free, Nouin Blade, and scatter!
76: I have your back, Yuwel! Hehe!
80:
You really wanted to say that line,
huh...
83:
Well then, I would leave my back to
no other, Your Highness.
91:
I hope you don't mind if we join in
too.
98:
Go, soldiers of Tris! Show the glory of
our might!
100:
We shan't be outdone by our
formidable allied adventurers! Lest I
return to my father in shame!
104:
Cieldeau! You didn't spare any
soldiers!
109:
Yours were not the only knights
eager to make a move.
112:
We are grateful to House Swes and
to you, Your Highness, for
masterfully giving us this
opportunity.
120:
Though born in different places,
under different circumstances, and
with seemingly different causes...
122:
People can always come together
as one.
125:
And unity will give them the power
to withstand anything.
129:
Now I see what our ideals meant,
Father...
136:
So, in the end, what is it that ya
wanted?
143:
Don't you try anythin' funny. We ain't
done talking yet.
147:
Hah... Haha... Is that the armor of the
Swallow Knights? You look ridiculous
in it...
150:
Are you sure you should be wasting
your time with me? You could be
fighting in the open and reclaiming
your honor as a knight instead.
154:
You think I care about any of that?
'Sides, the others can handle
themselves just fine.
175:
I could tell you, but it would be
meaningless. You and I will never
come to an understanding.
183:
Oh, just shut up already! I told you
there's no point!
186:
You're the most annoying brat I've
ever met! You wanna know my
plan? Are you stupid? It's the most
obvious thing in the world!
190:
Revenge against the Oxtans... Is that
it?
194:
To that end, you wanted to spread
fear and hostility toward them.
196:
The Kweturs aren't even a factor.
You only wish to harm the Oxtans.
204:
Of course you're right! I have to
prove it! I must prove it!
209:
I must prove that the Oxtans, Eighth
House and protectors of Farlana, are
rotten to the core!
217: What are you trying to do?!
224:
Don't you understand? The Oxtans
are no less than the scum of the
land! They would raise their hand
against the royal family if it meant
saving their own skins!
227:
They are corrupting our light!
Contaminating our faith!
231:
Follow this path, and you won't be
any different than them, Marden!
236:
Of course I'm not! It's too late for me!
Unlike all of you, I was born an Oxtan!
240: That's why I'll end it all here and now!
245:
I beseech you, Devourer of Stars!
Consume this tainted light of mine!
261:
What're you kids standing around
for?! I could use a hand!
276:
Tch! Just had to go and make my
job even harder, didn't ya?!
282:
Haha... Hahaha! What fearsome
strength! All that's left is...
